com.interpss.core.aclf.hvdc

Interface HvdcLine2T

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Branch, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfAdjustment, IAdaptable, IBranchSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BaseHvdcLine2TVSC<TBus>, HvdcLine2TCCC, HvdcLine2TVSC, HvdcLine2TVSCDyn, HvdcLine2TVSCDynPlus
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseHvdcLine2TVSCImpl, HvdcLine2TCCCImpl, HvdcLine2TImpl, HvdcLine2TVSCDynImpl, HvdcLine2TVSCImpl

    public interface HvdcLine2T
extends Branch, IAclfAdjustment
    A representation of the model object 'Hvdc Line2 T'. Always assume fromBus(rectifier) -> toBus(invetor)

    The following features are supported:

    • Rdc
    • Mva Rating
    • Imax
    See Also:
    HvdcLinePackage.getHvdcLine2T()
